{"tid":1344184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"收集緊元朗文宣素材，求大家幫幫手。","createTime":"2019-07-21T20:53:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T03:20:15.000Z","uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1bd44b7503e5349b46cf1858efc4910c33311f15","tid":1344184,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:53:22.000Z","msg":"小弟整緊段影片，想整合全部元朗黑社會打人影片，因有現階段網上多數有關影片未有整合不利傳播，而且見到部份youtube影片試圖以元朗村民擊退示威者試圖騎劫/合理化黑社會暴力行為，所想收集傷者圖片/影片，暫時只有柳俊江果張相，希望各位幫幫手。<br />\n<br />\n暫時打人果d影片已經收集好，不過除左傷者圖片/影片，其他你覺得可能有用既都可以放上黎，我盡睇。<br />\n<br />\n小弟聽日唔返工今晚唔訓無所謂，只想整好段片聽朝可以拿拿聲比向位傳出去~今晚係有好多唔知咩事一早訓左既人，希望佢地比其他人誤導前可以得到正確資訊，求大家幫幫手。"},{"pid":"9f5264dc103c16100a51c8ff903f4eb846db0f3e","tid":1344184,"uid":227271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:54:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd043baaff92a1f01282bf8be5cc7f5fd95645ce","tid":1344184,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:56:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beed5a884cfd811dbae938737ca54468849bfa89","tid":1344184,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b44bcd09a7ffae23ffbb584d6cf40ecf237f02","tid":1344184,"uid":219277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:58:32.000Z","msg":"立場姐姐<br />\n仲有個好早俾人打 背脊一堆藤條/鐵枝印嘅男士 好似俾01影左相？<br />\n仲有now話自己派出去嘅記者被打 仲有掉爆左一部cam"},{"pid":"a8c2356eb61f03d858542a5042598ca1b5ad21c8","tid":1344184,"uid":227271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:58:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"948cb6fd4291291725fe8880f9166046e1053264","tid":1344184,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T20:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QwqaCfU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQwqaCfU.png&h=3